{"body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"requesturi\">\n<span id=\"id1\"></span><h1>requestUri</h1>\n<p>Access the full URI of the request.</p>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"signature\">\n<h2>Signature</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight-scala\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span class=\"k\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">requestUri</span><span class=\"k\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Directive1</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">Uri</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> \n</pre></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"description\">\n<h2>Description</h2>\n<p>Use <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../../scheme-directives/#schemedirectives\"><em>SchemeDirectives</em></a>, <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../../host-directives/#hostdirectives\"><em>HostDirectives</em></a>, <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../../path-directives/#pathdirectives\"><em>PathDirectives</em></a>,  and <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../../parameter-directives/#parameterdirectives\"><em>ParameterDirectives</em></a> for more\ntargeted access to parts of the URI.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"example\">\n<h2>Example</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight-scala\"><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span class=\"k\">val</span> <span class=\"n\">route</span> <span class=\"k\">=</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">requestUri</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span> <span class=\"n\">uri</span> <span class=\"k\">=&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">complete</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">s</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;Full URI: $uri&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"nc\">Get</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;/&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">~&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">route</span> <span class=\"o\">~&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">check</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"c1\">// tests are executed with the host assumed to be &quot;example.com&quot;</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">responseAs</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">String</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">===</span> <span class=\"s\">&quot;Full URI: http://example.com/&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"o\">}</span>\n<span class=\"nc\">Get</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;/test&quot;</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">~&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">route</span> <span class=\"o\">~&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">check</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">responseAs</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"kt\">String</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">===</span> <span class=\"s\">&quot;Full URI: http://example.com/test&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"o\">}</span>\n</pre></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n", "display_toc": true, "title": "requestUri", "sourcename": "", "customsidebar": null, "current_page_name": "documentation/spray-routing/misc-directives/requestUri", "next": {"link": "../rewriteUnmatchedPath/", "title": "rewriteUnmatchedPath"}, "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["documentation/spray-routing/misc-directives/rewriteUnmatchedPath", "rewriteUnmatchedPath", "N", "next"], ["documentation/spray-routing/misc-directives/requestInstance", "requestInstance", "P", "previous"]], "meta": {}, "parents": [{"link": "../../../", "title": "Documentation"}, {"link": "../../", "title": "spray-routing"}, {"link": "../../predefined-directives-by-trait/", "title": "Predefined Directives (by trait)"}, {"link": "../", "title": "MiscDirectives"}], "sidebars": null, "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">requestUri</a><ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#signature\">Signature</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#description\">Description</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#example\">Example</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n", "prev": {"link": "../requestInstance/", "title": "requestInstance"}, "metatags": ""}